@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gwdsis(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v0
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs((v2 + 0.48 * v0 + 0.68)))
    v0 = wp.sin(tmp)
    tmp = v1
    v1 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.75) / v1) / tmp)
    v0 = (tmp * (tmp + (v2 + 0.26 + v1 + 0.20)))
    data[tid] = v0
